headline.print_headline: Amgen Profit Falls on Costs, Disappointing Sales
headline.main: Amgen Profit Falls on Costs, Disappointing Sales

lead_paragraph: Amgen Inc on Tuesday reported lower first quarter profit as results were hurt by acquisition-related costs as well as sales of several key products that fell short of Wall Street estimates.
